trans-unit.source: A set of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageQuery" /> objects and an associated string parameter.
trans-unit.target: Um conjunto de objetos <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageQuery" /> e um parâmetro de cadeia de caracteres associado.

trans-unit.source: A correlation hash (<see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceKey" />) is computed from the results of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageQuery" /> objects as well as the associated strings.
trans-unit.target: Um hash de correlação (<see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceKey" />) é computado dos resultados dos objetos <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageQuery" />, bem como as cadeias de caracteres associadas.
